DONUT DONUT DONUT

Donuts are a type of pastry that is shaped like a ring with a hole in the middle, a donut made of flour, sugar, eggs, and butter which are made into dough and given yeast to expand the dough at a glance donuts are almost similar to bread but donuts are also similar to cakes

Donuts have stuffing in them such as cream, jam, jelly and many more. donuts also have toppings on it as a decoration or tamahan so donuts look delicious like sprinkles of sugar, liquid chocolate, chocolate granules, cream and others

Donuts have spread all over the world and many who likes the food. There are many companies that produce donuts even in every country has its own variant of donuts
